016    package org.kuali.kfs.module.external.kc.service;
017    import javax.jws.WebService;
018    import javax.jws.soap.SOAPBinding;
019    
020    import org.kuali.kfs.integration.cg.ContractsAndGrantsConstants;
021    
022    
023    @WebService(name = ContractsAndGrantsConstants.RiceApplicationConfigurationService.WEB_SERVICE_NAME, 
024                targetNamespace = ContractsAndGrantsConstants.MODULE_TARGET_NAMESPACE)
025    @SOAPBinding(style = SOAPBinding.Style.DOCUMENT, use = SOAPBinding.Use.LITERAL, 
026                 parameterStyle = SOAPBinding.ParameterStyle.WRAPPED)
027    
028    public interface KcRiceApplicationConfigurationService {
029        /**
030         * @see org.kuali.rice.kns.service.RiceApplicationConfigurationService#getBaseInquiryUrl(java.lang.String)
031         */
032        public String getBaseInquiryUrl(String businessObjectClassName);
033    
034        /**
035         * @see org.kuali.rice.kns.service.RiceApplicationConfigurationService#getBaseLookupUrl(java.lang.String)
036         */
037        public String getBaseLookupUrl(String businessObjectClassName);
038    
039        
040        public String getBaseHelpUrl(String businessObjectClassName);
041    
042    }
